creator: Charles Darwin
description:
LibriVox recording of The Origin Of Species by Natural Selection by Charles Darwin.
Read in English by Michael Armenta
This is the 6th and last edition of "On The Origin of Species" with all additions and corrections, often considered the Definitive Edition.
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
subject: librivox; audiobooks;animals; biology; genetics; evolution
